Treasuries-only portfolios are designed for investors who need monthly cash returns with ultra-low price volatility. Currently targeting 3% cash returns with treasuries of less than 5-year maturities. The annual fee rate is 0.25% with a $1,000,000 minimum.

[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_3" _builder_version="4.16" global_colors_info="{}"][et_pb_image src="https://www.vierawealth.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/financial-advisor-icon-111x.png" _builder_version="4.16" locked="off" global_colors_info="{}"][/et_pb_image][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.18.0" header_4_font="Darker Grotesque|900|||||||" header_4_font_size="22px" custom_margin="||20px||false|false" custom_padding="||10px||false|false" border_width_bottom="2px" locked="off" global_colors_info="{}"]

[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_3" _builder_version="4.16" global_colors_info="{}"][et_pb_image src="https://www.vierawealth.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/financial-advisor-icon-61x.png" _builder_version="4.16" locked="off" global_colors_info="{}"][/et_pb_image][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.18.0" header_4_font="Darker Grotesque|900|||||||" header_4_font_size="22px" custom_margin="||20px||false|false" custom_padding="||10px||false|false" border_width_bottom="2px" locked="off" global_colors_info="{}"]

Cash-flow

Cash-flow portfolios target 4.5% interest and dividend cash returns in a mixture of treasuries, stocks, bonds, ETFs, mutual funds, and other securities. Designed for those with monthly cash needs who can tolerate market volatility. The annual fee rate is 0.60% with a $500,000 minimum.
